 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/native_client/trunk/src/native_client/src/trusted/validator_ragel/unreviewed/validator-x86_64.rl?r1=7824&amp;r2=7823&amp;pathrev=7824

validator_ragel: Unify validator test diagnostics.

Preceding to error message print the hex offset of the *beginning* byte of the
instruction, where an error occurred.  This allows processing validator output
uniformly for running the tests coming from the old validator.

Also, make it possible in a later change to continue after error, i.e. avoid
direct calls to exit(3).

